{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/combine-two-arrays-using-the-concat-method","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"functional-programming","demoType":null,"title":"Povežite dve linije podataka pomoću metode concat","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><dfn>Concatenation</dfn> to znači spajanje stvari kraj na kraj. JavaScript pruža način da se <code>concat</code> za nizove karaktera i nizove podataka koji rade na isti način. Za nizove podataka, ova metoda se poziva na jedan, a zatim drugi niz se prosleđuje kao argument za <code>concat</code>, koji se dodaje na kraj prvog niza. Vraća novi niz i ne izaziva nikakve promene u prvobitnim nizovima. Evo primera:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">[1, 2, 3].concat([4, 5, 6]);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Vraćeni red će biti <code>[1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d7da9367417b2b2512b66","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristi putanju <code>concat</code> u funkciji <code>nonMutatingConcat</code> da spoji <code>attach</code> na kraj <code>original</code>. Funkcija treba vratiti spojeni red.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301229,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/combine-two-arrays-using-the-concat-method"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function nonMutatingConcat(original, attach) {\r\n  // Only change code below this line\r\n\r\n\r\n  // Only change code above this line\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst first = [1, 2, 3];\r\nconst second = [4, 5];\r\nnonMutatingConcat(first, second);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Tvoj kod bi trebalo da koristi metodu <code>concat</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/\\.concat/g));"},{"text":"<p>Safu od <code>first</code> ne sme da se menja.</p>","testString":"assert(JSON.stringify(first) === JSON.stringify([1, 2, 3]));"},{"text":"<p>Reda <code>second</code> ne bi trebalo da se menja.</p>","testString":"assert(JSON.stringify(second) === JSON.stringify([4, 5]));"},{"text":"<p><code>nonMutatingConcat([1, 2, 3], [4, 5])</code> treba da vrati <code>[1, 2, 3, 4, 5]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(\r\n  JSON.stringify(nonMutatingConcat([1, 2, 3], [4, 5])) ===\r\n    JSON.stringify([1, 2, 3, 4, 5])\r\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#functional-programming","dashedName":"combine-two-arrays-using-the-concat-method","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"functional-programming","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/add-elements-to-the-end-of-an-array-using-concat-instead-of-push","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/remove-elements-from-an-array-using-slice-instead-of-splice","id":"587d7da9367417b2b2512b66","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"const add = x => y => z => x + y + z","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/combine-two-arrays-using-the-concat-method"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"